    "While the underlying neurophysiological mechanisms leading to this difference remain unidentified, these results point to a potential origin of visceral dysregulation (and perhaps its influence on maladaptive behavior) across multiple psychiatric conditions.",
    "This represents an important step towards a primary goal of computational psychiatry-computationally phenotyping individuals with psychiatric disorders with the tools of computational neuroscience in hopes of using this information to guide the development of precision medicine interventions.",
